{"id": 2701, "genre": 1004, "title": "你的“电子设备叛逆”到什么程度了？", "description": "我的 iPhone 一直在努力让我变成更好的人，但它败了。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 13790, "comment_count": 85, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181227172410Iai76OgKHVGohCvT.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 6, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-12-31T17:00:00Z", "column": null, "normal_questions": [{"id": 5133, "content": "系统软件提示安装更新，你通常选啥？", "image": "img/question/question/20181229102310quI5dz6EO8PnHhj0.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 319125, "title": "立即重启安装", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 319126, "title": "稍后尝试", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 319127, "title": "明天提醒我", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5134, "content": "App 尝试和你推心置腹：要想及时接到消息提醒请开推送，你会？", "image": "img/question/question/20181229102319B5Lms91py2ROh6Qd.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 319128, "title": "知道了，开了！", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 319129, "title": "好吧，但你要乱发我还是会取消的", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 319130, "title": "不行，想得美", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5135, "content": "备用浏览器总是想上位成为默认浏览器，你会？", "image": "img/question/question/20181229102333wLqATE2GD5RICHg8.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 319131, "title": "没留神点了同意，用完再改设置", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 319132, "title": "不准，问一次拒绝一次", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 319133, "title": "行吧，那默认你好了", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5136, "content": "Kindle 上看到有人标记的段落，你更有可能？", "image": "img/question/question/20181229102344G0vfE6MXqyuZNnAr.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 319134, "title": "这有啥的，不值得我标", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 319135, "title": "果然说得好，我也标记一下", "score": 0.0, "image": null}, {"id": 319136, "title": "虽然还不错，但我选择标旁边这句", "score": 0.0, "image": null}]}, {"id": 5137, "content": "游戏防沉迷系统触发“您累计在线时间已满3小时，请您下线休息”时，你会？ ", "image": "img/question/question/20181229102359Wp9EgqKJNuyx3oHY.gif", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 319138, "title": "忙于战斗，没看清就关了", "score": 0.0, "image": n